{"ja421:0.1":"Jataka ","ja421:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","ja421:0.3":"Kaccanivagga ","ja421:0.4":"5. Gangamalajataka ","ja421:1.1":"“Angarajata pathavi, ","ja421:1.2":"kukkulanugata mahi; ","ja421:1.3":"Atha gayasi vattani, ","ja421:1.4":"na tam tapati atapo. ","ja421:2.1":"Uddham tapati adicco, ","ja421:2.2":"adho tapati valuka; ","ja421:2.3":"Atha gayasi vattani, ","ja421:2.4":"na tam tapati atapo”. ","ja421:3.1":"“Na mam tapati atapo, ","ja421:3.2":"atapa tapayanti mam; ","ja421:3.3":"Attha hi vividha raja, ","ja421:3.4":"te tapanti na atapo”. ","ja421:4.1":"“Addasam kama te mulam, ","ja421:4.2":"sankappa kama jayasi; ","ja421:4.3":"Na tam sankappayissami, ","ja421:4.4":"evam kama na hehisi”. ","ja421:5.1":"“Appapi kama na alam, ","ja421:5.2":"bahuhipi na tappati; ","ja421:5.3":"Ahaha balalapana, ","ja421:5.4":"parivajjetha jaggato”. ","ja421:6.1":"“Appassa kammassa phalam mamedam, ","ja421:6.2":"Udayo ajjhagama mahattapattam; ","ja421:6.3":"Suladdhalabho vata manavassa, ","ja421:6.4":"Yo pabbaji kamaragam pahaya”. ","ja421:7.1":"“Tapasa pajahanti papakammam, ","ja421:7.2":"Tapasa nhapitakumbhakarabhavam; ","ja421:7.3":"Tapasa abhibhuyya gangamala, ","ja421:7.4":"Namenalapasajja brahmadattam”. ","ja421:8.1":"“Sanditthikameva ‘amma’ passatha, ","ja421:8.2":"Khantisoraccassa ayam vipako; ","ja421:8.3":"Yo sabbajanassa vanditohu, ","ja421:8.4":"Tam vandama sarajika samacca”. ","ja421:9.1":"“Ma kinci avacuttha gangamalam, ","ja421:9.2":"Muninam monapathesu sikkhamanam; ","ja421:9.3":"Eso hi atari annavam, ","ja421:9.4":"Yam taritva caranti vitasoka”ti. ","ja421:10.1":"Gangamalajatakam pancamam. "}